<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="dev" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Full-Stack Engineering</h2>
		<p>Experienced in building scalable web and mobile applications using React, Node.js, Spring Boot, Kotlin, and Swift. Passionate about clean architecture and reusable components.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="automation" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>DevOps Automation</h2>
		<p>Skilled in Docker, GitHub Actions, Jenkins, and Kubernetes. I automate CI/CD pipelines and deploy cloud-native applications to AWS and GCP with best practices.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="smartphone" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Cross-Platform Mobile</h2>
		<p>Developed Android (Kotlin) and iOS (SwiftUI) apps with Firebase integration. Focused on modern UI, MVVM architecture, and push notifications for better UX.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="problem-solver" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Problem Solver</h2>
		<p>Passionate about solving engineering pain points. I build developer tools and dashboards that improve team productivity and system observability.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="cloud-native" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Cloud Native</h2>
		<p>Deploying services on AWS (EC2, Lambda, S3) and Firebase. Comfortable working with infrastructure-as-code (Terraform) and microservice architecture.</p>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="lifelong-learner" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Lifelong Learner</h2>
		<p>I constantly explore new tech: recently diving into Astro, GraphQL, Supabase, and AI agents. Learning is embedded in how I grow as a developer.</p>
	</div>
</section>


<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
